{"tid":1592351,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】《在台港生同盟成立宣言》","createTime":"2019-09-24T14:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T03:20:19.000Z","uid":258069,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"1dbeb57ca8e290f70eb7eb6f3f6e80d601f09178","tid":1592351,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"《在台港生同盟成立宣言》<br />\n<br />\n我哋係一個由喺台灣讀書遍及各個職業嘅手足組成嘅組織。由6.9到今日，我哋一直喺各個領域同大家同行。無奈地到咗九月，我哋必須要返臺灣開學，遠離我哋嘅屋企同革命主戰場&mdash;香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺義守大學事件後，我哋發現香港僑生喺臺灣嘅自由並未有保障。手足响遭到大陸學生攻擊後，相關學校高層居然包庇大陸學生，甚至要滅手足聲；中華民國警察不願意為手足落案，誘導手足同大陸學生和解，以致地檢署無法落案；各個政黨以至政府部門都未有明確協助呢一班手足。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢一群大陸學生破壞咗《中華民國憲法》賦予我哋喺臺灣嘅言論自由；義守大學包庇大陸學生使佢哋可以「低調處理」，免於法律制裁，完全係使到香港僑生喺臺灣嘅安全得唔到保障。我哋更加相信，大陸人嘅狂妄自大將會進一步對臺灣人同香港人有更進一步嘅威脅。因此，除咗將香港僑生組織起嚟之外，我哋希望可以得到更多臺灣學生關注，同臺灣人一齊對抗「赤納粹 Chinazi」响臺灣蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋組織會堅持自革命開始以嚟冇大台嘅原則，我哋所有人只有一個身份&mdash;在台港生。我哋組織唔會推舉同選立一位領袖，正如連登一樣，我哋只係一個畀有共同目標嘅香港僑生聯絡嘅平臺，使到臺灣有更多人關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n「在台港生同盟」成立宗旨<br />\n<br />\n我哋以「兄弟爬山，各自努力」，自主自為嘅前鋒精神支持依場運動。推動臺灣學生對於香港自6.9以嚟因反送中所發生嘅慘劇加以關注。監察臺灣在地有關香港學生團體對响香港事務嘅實際援助支持，核心使命包括：<br />\n<br />\n一、喺臺灣以行動支援香港反送中運動，成功之前絕不放棄。<br />\n<br />\n二、為有需要嘅在台港生提供政治協助。<br />\n<br />\n三、推動臺灣全民對抗「赤納粹 Chinazi」<br />\n<br />\n四、確保有關台灣在地香港學生組織嘅運行，能夠切實可行幫助相關人士。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n在台港生同盟<br />\n#216979 鬚蜥 #260823 龍和道上將 #82633 串過馬撚 #272469 假台妹真港女 #258069 越南仔"},{"pid":"79498f12fd2d692731b868b32e962d96cae4ba63","tid":1592351,"uid":47605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"41e96e9bc2738ff2456681917758c0aeeb77192a","tid":1592351,"uid":260823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"88783ca40e00f07a035ab7d61daff887c9ed3eb4","tid":1592351,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"好，支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n許個願啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果聽日有雙普選，你會想做乜？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592301</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b72365da07fcdecffc8e323a45cb38961724449","tid":1592351,"uid":263680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"[下一步升級行動] 點解唔可以有第二次佔中?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592335</a>"},{"pid":"dfdeccc53c0784518e024f03d9ad1b828d9481a2","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"台灣都有好多手足需要幫忙<br />\n希望香港嘅手足可以留意下<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n煲底見"},{"pid":"7a613ae5ef87730f46da35507f52bff5276207cf","tid":1592351,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2bde490f6e7423a7bac66948f6c31d94747fd3","tid":1592351,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee7d59f52f53647a73b5e1bcb7112545de0f1ec","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"10連推"},{"pid":"2bb9c958dabdee798be081bc854b3fe3b43b29f7","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:37:04.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"39ebff32f00be2eb3fb5c0e179f65d594fef5f73","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"b5afa9e9a86a1323a71cddbb65a20b8a2e6b1845","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:37:27.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"ee3e886a57368d92c112958aa3a04e569f509e8e","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"6453670bee8289856ff29305394f31aaf593bf56","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"6ac02f561bb81f455b8e4b4592b441ab0ea93aad","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"0f2b77947c3867b099344b457d42dcee4f574994","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"612857fe0c621c5bd85cfeaa779f0915e3bede4d","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8a9e8d8cb9286b49aafec399af18c4f6001eb0ac","tid":1592351,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609c214730e7e7dd7b9e95900b1175bfed80a330","tid":1592351,"uid":140710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8725954fef419128b0a08a6fcafd6eef8460a894","tid":1592351,"uid":216979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0b145de9fd0302ba63bebce68773c323acd85b0a","tid":1592351,"uid":106580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"加油！搞大件事俾蔡英文知 選票唔係咁易賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ffc12f1f62918314d224cb841752b5a36a3ab8","tid":1592351,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"我覺得最重要係connect台灣人，始終係人地地方，唔好喧賓奪主（班支那人就係去到邊都圍威喂搞到全世人都憎佢）"},{"pid":"13565e081b4fb618a5f504478e4aaf3ae4ed38e8","tid":1592351,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:39:17.000Z","msg":"有冇得將班支那學生同韓國瑜扯埋一齊？"},{"pid":"06f87cc840bd4ca78836fc0d7a51f7a340bc3663","tid":1592351,"uid":272469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"P牌無得推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊加油！"},{"pid":"bef7bc690735b7865f17064c56a66a6192abf89f","tid":1592351,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"我哋啲手足好多P牌 幫幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2cf7b2e9eec6df466852a3d6d7bcd806da4504","tid":1592351,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc45f9b2b92b0aeba91e934e6eb27dedf3a607f","tid":1592351,"uid":193786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:47:07.000Z","msg":"support"},{"pid":"b510438625d6ac1c61b5358211acb4acda7b8cf7","tid":1592351,"uid":242349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:48:59.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"bc1651d7dcbf4e8152a934bb958485baa20ad43f","tid":1592351,"uid":109629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"龍和道上將<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個名又幾有霸氣"},{"pid":"307d695d21aaecf977602760b7eb514e4886e35c","tid":1592351,"uid":184985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:54:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adbc9711216716f7609ff0df2c31dfff76220877","tid":1592351,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"《在台港生同盟成立宣言 華文版》<br />\n<br />\n我們是一個由在臺灣留學，在革命中遍及不同崗位的學生組成的組織。由六月九日至今，我們一直與香港人同行，無奈到了九月，我們必須要回臺灣開學，離開我們的家和革命主戰場&mdash;香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在義守大學事件之後，我們發現香港學生在臺灣的自由並未有受到保障。港生在遭到大陸學生攻擊後，相關學校高層居然包庇大陸學生，甚至要他們噤聲；中華民國警察不願意為港生落案，誘導香港學生同大陸學生和解，以致地檢署無法落案；各個政黨以至政府部門都未有明確協助這一群香港學生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這一群大陸學生破壞了《中華民國憲法》賦予我們在臺灣的言論自由；義守大學包庇大陸學生使他們可以「低調處理」，免於法律制裁，完全係使到香港學生在臺灣的安全得不到保障。我們更加相信，大陸人的狂妄自大將會進一步對臺灣人同香港人有更進一步的威脅。因此，除了將香港僑生組織起來之外，我們希望可以得到更多臺灣學生關注，同臺灣人一起對抗「赤納粹 Chinazi」在臺灣蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們組織會堅持自革命開始以來沒大台主導的原則，我們所有人只有一個身份&mdash;在台港生。我們組織不會推舉同選立一位領袖，正如香港連登一樣，我們只是一個給有共同目標的香港僑生聯絡的平臺，使到臺灣有更多人關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n「在台港生同盟」成立宗旨<br />\n<br />\n我們以「兄弟爬山，各自努力」，自主自為的前鋒精神支持這場運動。推動臺灣學生對於香港自6.9以來因反送中所發生的慘劇加以關注。監察臺灣在地有關香港學生團體對於香港事務的實際援助支持，核心使命包括：<br />\n<br />\n一、在臺灣以行動支援香港反送中運動，成功之前絕不放棄。<br />\n<br />\n二、為有需要的在台港生提供政治協助。<br />\n<br />\n三、推動臺灣全民對抗「赤納粹 Chinazi」<br />\n<br />\n四、確保有關台灣在地香港學生組織嘅運行，能夠切實可行幫助相關人士。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n在台港生同盟<br />\n#216979 鬚蜥 #260823 龍和道上將 #82633 串過馬撚 #272469 假台妹真港女 #258069 越南仔"},{"pid":"a8787bb2a00a39fcfd19da6b207855ba8cc520e1","tid":1592351,"uid":162969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5943e88fc7e978ddd25de96ad31719d9c411fb47","tid":1592351,"uid":82633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n我地都係求救無門後逼於無奈出黎既組織<br />\n鑑於越來越多在台手足發生被欺凌、被噤聲狀況<br />\n而台灣目前只得一個香港組織 &mdash; 香港邊青<br />\n呢個組織可以提供既能力極之有限<br />\n義守手足一事佢地都係冷處理甚至話係「好小事姐」敷衍了事<br />\n所以希望有個組織可以比其他有同樣情況既在台港人聯繫、求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3d0a18acaf6f272bd579220b7070fcbb21e452","tid":1592351,"uid":82633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"767cc9bce42b2788354f7b2f14bc8b7cb365a30f","tid":1592351,"uid":82633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:39:19.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"128e19fc999c2f842999a00c25a186be65aa6d98","tid":1592351,"uid":82633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"4ec8e9144ca5ee5980095ce9a1ce57fd95ee7a86","tid":1592351,"uid":82633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:40:25.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"14a0fb6cc098755ec5b46c898a69595779540e25","tid":1592351,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第六期牆紙］ 百日抗爭運動，願榮光終歸香港<br />\n第六期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1583745/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1583745/page/1</a><br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link 